transcripts.text: Hey guys, welcome to Liberty University.  My name is Tatum.

And I'm Carter.  We're currently right outside of the main dining hall here at Liberty University, the Reber Thomas Dining Hall.  We have plenty of different options for our students to have, anything from rise and shine all-day breakfast to Mexican-style Mongolian grill and even Italian.  We have plenty of different desserts for you to also have as well.

Yeah, and a way that you can get that food is through our two different dining plans.  In those dining plans, you get unlimited swipes to this dining hall that's open all day, as well as Flames cash and dining dollars every semester that you can use at other locations.  So you have lots of options here on campus when it comes to eating.
